text: Hi tom nice to meet you, Ive been thinking a lot and I real do feel like going in the RAF is what I want to do either doing logistics or military police. Did you have a good time in the military and would you recommend it to people? I do know people who've been in but who are quite a bit older so I'm wondering how it was for you being closer to my age. Also how was coming out of military life and going into the real world?
